title: Chocolate
body: Chocolate doesn't ask questions. Chocolate understands.

title: Eleanor
body: No one can make you feel inferior without your consent
author: Eleanor Roosevelt

title: Queen
body: Think like a queen. A queen is not afraid to fail. Failure is another steppingstone to greatness.
author: Oprah Winfrey

title: Crayons
body: I consider myself a crayon, I might not be your favorite color but one day you'll need me to complete your picture.
author: Savannah Highnote

title: Sleeping
body: The future is shaped by your dreams, so stop wasting time and go to sleep! - Some one who loves sleeping
author: A lover of Sleep
